description: Open since June of 2010, The Chubby Chickpea is a fast, fun and friendly way to enjoy authentic Israeli style Middle Eastern food with modern twists! Specializing in fresh Falafel and featuring an entire menu of home-made goods, the Chickpea serves lunch and dinner six days each week. The Chickpea also has a catering menu and mobile food truck that can meet the needs of groups of all sizes.  All of our catering platters can be customized and our food truck can serve parties of all sizes. If you want healthy, fast and fresh, look no further than The Chubby Chickpea!
name: The Chubby Chickpea Mobile
